{"tid":1760942,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇對一件死物好有感情？","createTime":"2019-11-28T14:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T04:44:56.000Z","uid":12836,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"b3738cb19d49aa960a87d81342efe7e6288b7b94","tid":1760942,"uid":12836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T14:28:37.000Z","msg":"我先 公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公仔真係俾我好大安全感<br />\n每次瞓覺都要靠佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後聽朝起身就發現我踢左佢落床<br />\n我仲會對住佢講 <br />\n對唔住呀踢咗你落去呵返先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我鍾意對住佢多過對住我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係每次要將我間房斷捨離嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩老都要求我要抌公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得有一次我要親手揼公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我特登用墊枱紙墊住個地下擺喺垃圾房<br />\n唔想整污糟佢 因為佢係我個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n離開垃圾房嘅時候我望返轉頭<br />\n隻公仔又望住我 好似唔捨得我走咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰日之後喊左兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家都仲係好掛住佢<br />\n唔知佢而家喺邊呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef6c88cb10fdaf29182e435a8340578db471d6d","tid":1760942,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"我都有wor"},{"pid":"e93213ceac6be2d481dffca3df05cc34120a24f0","tid":1760942,"uid":12836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"等待20歲A0毒撚的到來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset